cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for graph convolutional networks, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The method involves transforming graph data into grid-like structures, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and signal processing (cs.SI). The paper also discusses model training on large-scale graphs, which is related to neural networks (cs.NE).
